{
  "title": "NiFi Overview",
  "description": "Cluster and JVM health, flow throughput, queue backpressure, repository storage, and bulletins for Apache NiFi.",
  "template_variables": [
    {
      "name": "host",
      "prefix": "host",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    },
    {
      "name": "nifi_version",
      "prefix": "nifi_version",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    },
    {
      "name": "process_group_name",
      "prefix": "process_group_name",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    },
    {
      "name": "source_name",
      "prefix": "source_name",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    }
  ],
  "layout_type": "ordered",
  "widgets": [
    {
      "definition": {
        "title": "About NiFi",
        "type": "group",
        "background_color": "white",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "image",
              "url": "/static/images/logos/nifi_large.svg",
              "sizing": "contain",
              "has_background": false,
              "has_border": false,
              "vertical_align": "center",
              "horizontal_align": "center"
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 6,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "note",
              "content": "## NiFi\n\nApache NiFi is a data-flow automation platform. This dashboard surfaces cluster and JVM health, flow throughput, queue backpressure, and repository storage, plus NiFi bulletins forwarded as Datadog events.\n\n### Useful links\n- [NiFi integration docs](https://docs.datadoghq.com/integrations/nifi/)\n- [Integration tile](/integrations/nifi)\n- [Apache NiFi documentation](https://nifi.apache.org/docs.html)",
              "background_color": "white",
              "font_size": "14",
              "text_align": "left",
              "show_tick": false,
              "tick_pos": "50%",
              "tick_edge": "left",
              "has_padding": true
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 2,
              "width": 6,
              "height": 4
            }
          }
        ],
        "show_title": true
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 6,
        "height": 7
      }
    },
    {
      "definition": {
        "title": "Overview",
        "type": "group",
        "background_color": "vivid_blue",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "definition": {
              "title": "Can connect",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "min:nifi.can_connect{$host}",
                      "aggregator": "min"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1"
                    }
                  ],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {
                      "comparator": ">=",
                      "value": 1,
                      "palette": "white_on_green"
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": "<",
                      "value": 1,
                      "palette": "white_on_red"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2,
              "timeseries_background": {
                "type": "bars"
              }
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 3,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "definition": {
              "title": "Heap utilization",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "avg:nifi.system.jvm.heap_utilization{$host,$nifi_version}",
                      "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1"
                    }
                  ],
                  "conditional_formats": [
                    {
                      "comparator": ">",
                      "value": 90,
                      "palette": "white_on_red"
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": ">",
                      "value": 75,
                      "palette": "white_on_yellow"
                    },
                    {
                      "comparator": "<=",
                      "value": 75,
                      "palette": "white_on_green"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2,
              "timeseries_background": {
                "type": "bars"
              }
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 3,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 3,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "definition": {
              "title": "Active threads",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "avg:nifi.flow.active_threads{$host,$nifi_version}",
                      "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2,
              "timeseries_background": {
                "type": "bars"
              }
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 2,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "definition": {
              "title": "Connected nodes",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "avg:nifi.cluster.connected_node_count{$host,$nifi_version}",
                      "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2,
              "timeseries_background": {
                "type": "bars"
              }
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 2,
              "y": 2,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "definition": {
              "title": "Total nodes",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_value",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "avg:nifi.cluster.total_node_count{$host,$nifi_version}",
                      "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "autoscale": true,
              "precision": 2,
              "timeseries_background": {
                "type": "bars"
              }
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 4,
              "y": 2,
              "width": 2,
              "height": 2
            }
          },
          {
            "definition": {
              "title": "NiFi version",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "query_table",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "avg:nifi.can_connect{$host,$nifi_version} by {nifi_version}",
                      "aggregator": "avg"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "scalar",
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1",
                      "limit": {
                        "count": 25,
                        "order": "desc"
                      },
                      "alias": "Reachable"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "has_search_bar": "auto"
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 4,
              "width": 6,
              "height": 2
            }
          }
        ],
        "show_title": true
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 6,
        "height": 7
      }
    },
    {
      "definition": {
        "title": "JVM Health",
        "type": "group",
        "background_color": "white",
        "layout_type": "ordered",
        "widgets": [
          {
            "definition": {
              "type": "note",
              "content": "JVM heap, garbage collection, and threads for the NiFi process. Watch heap utilization trending toward 100% and rising GC time \u2014 both signal memory pressure that can stall the flow.",
              "background_color": "white",
              "font_size": "14",
              "text_align": "left",
              "show_tick": false,
              "tick_pos": "50%",
              "tick_edge": "left",
              "has_padding": true
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 12,
              "height": 1
            }
          },
          {
            "definition": {
              "title": "Heap used vs max",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "avg:nifi.system.jvm.heap_used{$host,$nifi_version}"
                    },
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query2",
                      "query": "avg:nifi.system.jvm.heap_max{$host,$nifi_version}"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "display_type": "line",
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1",
                      "alias": "Heap used"
                    },
                    {
                      "formula": "query2",
                      "alias": "Heap max"
                    }
                  ],
                  "style": {
                    "palette": "dog_classic",
                    "line_type": "solid",
                    "line_width": "normal"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "legend_columns": [
                "avg",
                "min",
                "max",
                "value",
                "sum"
              ],
              "legend_layout": "auto"
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 0,
              "y": 1,
              "width": 6,
              "height": 3
            }
          },
          {
            "definition": {
              "title": "Heap utilization",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "avg:nifi.system.jvm.heap_utilization{$host,$nifi_version}"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "display_type": "line",
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1",
                      "alias": "Heap utilization"
                    }
                  ],
                  "style": {
                    "palette": "dog_classic",
                    "line_type": "solid",
                    "line_width": "normal"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "legend_columns": [
                "avg",
                "min",
                "max",
                "value",
                "sum"
              ],
              "legend_layout": "auto",
              "markers": [
                {
                  "value": "y = 90",
                  "display_type": "error dashed",
                  "label": "Critical"
                },
                {
                  "value": "y = 75",
                  "display_type": "warning dashed",
                  "label": "Warning"
                }
              ]
            },
            "layout": {
              "x": 6,
              "y": 1,
              "width": 6,
              "height": 3
            }
          },
          {
            "definition": {
              "title": "GC collections",
              "title_size": "16",
              "title_align": "left",
              "type": "timeseries",
              "requests": [
                {
                  "queries": [
                    {
                      "data_source": "metrics",
                      "name": "query1",
                      "query": "sum:nifi.system.gc.collection_count{$host,$nifi_version} by {gc_name}.as_count()"
                    }
                  ],
                  "response_format": "timeseries",
                  "display_type": "bars",
                  "formulas": [
                    {
                      "formula": "query1",
